# PCAP Analysis

## Goal
Analyze network traffic and identify suspicious connections or behavior.

## Tools
- Wireshark
- Volatility

## What I did
- reviewed captured network traffic;
- checked source and destination IP addresses;
- analyzed protocols and packets;
- searched for suspicious requests;
- compared network activity with the incident timeline.

## Result
- found suspicious network connections;
- identified signs of unusual traffic.

## Conclusion
Learned the basics of PCAP analysis.
